<P>POETICAL Meditations, BEING THE IMPROVEMENT OF SOME <HI>Vacant Hours,</HI> By ROGER WOLCOTT, <HI><ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR></HI> WITH A PREFACE By the REVEREND Mr. <HI>Bulkley</HI> of <HI>Colche&s;ter. <HI>NEW LONDON:</HI></HI> Printed and Sold by <HI>T. Green,</HI> 1725.</P>
